{"tid":1579310,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"尋一恐怖片(童年回憶)","createTime":"2019-09-18T13:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T15:04:27.000Z","uid":167251,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c110d8d673d2734e21e4b92989f1166b611aae19","tid":1579310,"uid":167251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"我沒有看過這套片,我只看過VCD封面,但我宜家好想睇,所以請求各位幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以下係我略略記得既野,可能都有小小唔同。<br />\n1.有位外國科學家類似被拋起,好似話死左<br />\n2.有隻類似怪既物體起封面,個封面寫住呢隻殺人既野究竟係人定係怪<br />\n3.有班白裙少女擺左個陣,似係作緊法,有好多蠟燭及火光起佢地中間<br />\n4.我起CD鋪見到呢隻碟,隻碟有中文字,我估計係日本/韓國片,我起2007年6月在某間CD鋪見到呢隻碟<br />\n5.我覺得似日本片,所以試過認真搵2000-2007年既日本恐怖片,但我搵唔到,所以求各位巴絲幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999,光復香港"},{"pid":"fbdd4ab87fe8f4185ae9035559b12fb4a55b531b","tid":1579310,"uid":167251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:55:32.000Z","msg":"求幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c49323dd8110a352234f055df3c8b4770f93b99","tid":1579310,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975602ed0ecb16cb2093e6f7b0d6d9b3d99a6b84","tid":1579310,"uid":167251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:08:43.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲知,人生遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f764eea1ee5749d63b5f6a933a4173028b7a63","tid":1579310,"uid":167251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56ee909743236e1846007447c12772ac21421df","tid":1579310,"uid":167251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7545b10573ede3359c2a49bf86e2d7ad7c6ada14","tid":1579310,"uid":33077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:42:33.000Z","msg":"難wo<br />\n香港既vcd 好多封面都自己edit 過<br />\n就算掃到你都可能因為封面而令你miss 左"},{"pid":"1ab5dec4aeaaccec56d4f06dfce6e614024e224e","tid":1579310,"uid":167251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"都有機會,但我起其他片有小小似我會睇,但都係冇發現,我主力搵香港上映過。btw,恐怖片有怪有科學家唔奇,但有班少女圍圈作法應該唔係好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望有巴絲睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5a8b3d341cb502ffb305ea066b4f607ce4bc0b","tid":1579310,"uid":167251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:25:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979d7c42e8f0952fae2e466b43a99f393323ca5e","tid":1579310,"uid":167251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9549d3783694d19dc4504901a2e15f25491e80","tid":1579310,"uid":167251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:02:25.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1580f4e39a7631a5c08888e4ce4320f2848e0d3c","tid":1579310,"uid":164043,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:07:00.000Z","msg":"少女？ 你點知唔係啊婆"},{"pid":"4967a30d9f799aac79fbd53c79d4eb6ff1f54a16","tid":1579310,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:10:45.000Z","msg":"一打開lift 啲怪物走曬出嚟食左成隊防暴隊嗰套"},{"pid":"ca4a2acbd456e68b929cf09d6ef3a1298111d471","tid":